title: Extortion How Politicians Extract Your Money, Buy Votes, and Lin
description:
What if the real problem in Washington isn't bribery'special interest lobbying'but extortion? What if we have been looking at political influence from the wrong end of the equation? What if the true blame lies with our politicians themselves? Extortion, by the author of the best-selling Throw Them All Out, reveals vast new areas of corruption in our political system. With eye-opening revelations on every page, it opens a whole new battlefield in the great war to fix what's wrong with our government.
Genre: Non Fiction , General
